<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.3">
<l>tārēṉ piṟarkkuṉ ṉaruḷeṉṉiṭai vaittāy</l>
<l>ārē ṉatuvē parukikkaḷik kiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>kārēy kaṭalē malaiyētiruk kōṭṭi</l>
<l>yūrē yukantā yaiyukantaṭi yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I did not give to others, [but] you bestowed your grace on me!</l>
<l>I, who am not [ever] satiated, drinking in that [grace], am intoxicated.</l>
<l>Rejoicing in you who rejoices in the cloud-like sea, the mountains,</l>
<l>And in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr, I am [your] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
